{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"vwa.la help","description":"Everything you need to know about the vwa.la influencer marketing platform."}},"ghostPost":{"title":"Google Forms","slug":"google-forms","featured":false,"feature_image":"https://docs.ghost.io/content/images/2018/09/google-forms.png","created_at_pretty":"20 September, 2018","published_at_pretty":"20 September, 2018","updated_at_pretty":"19 November, 2018","created_at":"2018-09-20T19:30:04.000+00:00","published_at":"2018-09-20T19:31:09.000+00:00","updated_at":"2018-11-19T11:57:18.000+00:00","excerpt":"Use Google Forms with Ghost as a free, embedded contact form to collect information from readers. ","meta_title":null,"meta_description":"Use Google Forms with Ghost as a free, embedded contact form to collect information from readers. Read more about Ghost integrations ⚡️","og_description":null,"og_image":null,"og_title":null,"twitter_description":null,"twitter_image":null,"twitter_title":null,"authors":[{"name":"John O'Nolan","slug":"john","bio":null,"profile_image":"//www.gravatar.com/avatar/f95828f4e92f1befebabfb7f65cdc8f2?s=250&d=mm&r=x","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":null}],"primary_author":{"name":"John O'Nolan","slug":"john","bio":null,"profile_image":"//www.gravatar.com/avatar/f95828f4e92f1befebabfb7f65cdc8f2?s=250&d=mm&r=x","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":null},"primary_tag":{"name":"Surveys & Forms","slug":"surveys-forms","description":null,"feature_image":null,"meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},"tags":[{"name":"Surveys & Forms","slug":"surveys-forms","description":null,"feature_image":null,"meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},{"name":"Card","slug":"card","description":null,"feature_image":null,"meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},{"name":"#integration","slug":"hash-integration","description":null,"feature_image":null,"meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"internal"}],"plaintext":"You can use Google Forms with Ghost as a free, embedded contact form to collect\ninformation from readers.\n\nWhether you just want to give people a way to contact you, or you're running a\nfull blown survey which you need to collect data for - Google Forms is a great\nway to support contact forms in Ghost. Getting a working form on your site\nshould take just a few minutes once you've finished making your form.\n\nTo get started, head over to Google Forms [https://forms.google.com]  and make a\nnew form.\n\nCreate a new form and send\nOnce you've customised the form to work how you'd like, click on the send\nbutton.\n\nGet the embed code from the send window\nFrom within the send window, select the Send via < >  tab, and copy the code\n\nWithin the Ghost editor, add an HTML card\nYou can paste the form code within an HTML card on any page to embed your form\n\nAdd some automation to submissions\nIf you'd like your form to work harder for you, it's also possible to add\nautomation by using Zapier [https://zapier.com]  to process your form\nsubmissions. Here are a few starting points to give you an idea of how to set\nthings up:","html":"<p>You can use Google Forms with Ghost as a free, embedded contact form to collect information from readers.</p><p>Whether you just want to give people a way to contact you, or you're running a full blown survey which you need to collect data for - Google Forms is a great way to support contact forms in Ghost. Getting a working form on your site should take just a few minutes once you've finished making your form.</p><p>To get started, head over to <a href=\"https://forms.google.com\">Google Forms</a> and make a new form.</p><h2 id=\"create-a-new-form-and-send\">Create a new form and send</h2><p>Once you've customised the form to work how you'd like, click on the send button.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://docs.ghost.io/content/images/2018/09/image-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><h2 id=\"get-the-embed-code-from-the-send-window\">Get the embed code from the send window</h2><p>From within the send window, select the <strong>Send via </strong><code>&lt; &gt;</code> tab, and copy the code</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://docs.ghost.io/content/images/2018/09/image-2.png\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><h2 id=\"within-the-ghost-editor-add-an-html-card\">Within the Ghost editor, add an HTML card</h2><p>You can paste the form code within an HTML card on any page to embed your form</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-wide\"><img src=\"https://docs.ghost.io/content/images/2018/09/image-3.png\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><h2 id=\"add-some-automation-to-submissions\">Add some automation to submissions</h2><p>If you'd like your form to work harder for you, it's also possible to add automation by using <a href=\"https://zapier.com\">Zapier</a> to process your form submissions. Here are a few starting points to give you an idea of how to set things up:</p><div id=\"zap\">\n    <script src=\"https://zapier.com/apps/embed/widget.js?services=google-forms&limit=8&html_id=zap\"></script>\n</div>","custom_template":null,"url":"https://docs.ghost.io/google-forms/","uuid":"196a16b2-1c1a-43a1-b15c-6bb58db59c5d","page":false,"codeinjection_foot":"","codeinjection_head":"","comment_id":"5ba3f53c06626b00bf6066ba"},"file":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":30,"height":30,"src":"/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/2682d/integration-icon.png","srcSet":"/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/2682d/integration-icon.png 1x,\n/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/0b300/integration-icon.png 1.5x,\n/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/5d50f/integration-icon.png 2x,\n/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/95621/integration-icon.png 3x"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"google-forms","relatedPosts":[{"node":{"slug":"typeform","title":"Typeform","url":"/integrations